    "Collect and disseminate metadata.",
    "Repositories of audio samples should include details of the study recruitment criteria and relevant metadata (for example, gender, age, symptoms, location, time since COVID-19 test) so that data can be filtered for quality and for relevance to hypothesis, and bias from measured confounders can be characterized and controlled if necessary. 2.",
    "Characterize and control recruitment bias.",
    "Analyse data using methods that acknowledge and control for the effects of recruitment bias.",
    "We approached this by matching on measured confounders in our test and/or training sets. 3."
